y of the [[Ultimate Fighting Championship]] (UFC), a [[mixed martial arts]] promotion based in the United States. In 2009 the UFC held 20 events beginning with, ''UFC 93: Franklin vs. Henderson''.\n\n{{TOClimit|2}}\n\n==Title fights==\n{{MMAtitle}}\n{{MMAtitle card|[[List of UFC champions|Title fights in 2009]]}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Welterweight\n| [[Georges St-Pierre]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[B.J. Penn]]\n| TKO (corner stoppage)\n| 4\n| 5:00\n| [[UFC 94]]\n| For the [[UFC Welterweight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Middleweight\n| [[Anderson Silva]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Thales Leites]]\n| Decision (unanimous) (49-46, 48-47, 50-46)\n| 5\n| 5:00\n| [[UFC 97]]\n| For the [[UFC Middleweight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Light Heavyweight\n| [[Lyoto Machida]]\n| def.\n| [[Rashad Evans]] (c)\n| KO (punches)\n| 2\n| 3:57\n| [[UFC 98]]\n| For the [[UFC Light Heavyweight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Welterweight\n| [[Georges St-Pierre]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Thiago Alves (fighter)|Thiago Alves]]\n| Decision (unanimous) (50\u201345, 50\u201344, 50\u201345)\n| 5\n| 5:00\n| [[UFC 100]]\n| For the [[UFC Welterweight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Heavyweight\n| [[Brock Lesnar]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Frank Mir]] (ic)\n| TKO (punches)\n| 2\n| 1:48\n| [[UFC 100]]\n| [[UFC Heavyweight Championship]] unification bout.\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Lightweight\n| [[B.J. Penn]] (c)\n| def\n| [[Kenny Florian]]\n| Submission (rear-naked choke)\n| 4\n| 3:54\n| [[UFC 101]]\n| For the [[UFC Lightweight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Light Heavyweight\n| [[Lyoto Machida]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Mauricio Rua]]\n| Decision (unanimous) (48-47, 48-47, 48-47)\n| 5\n| 5:00\n| [[UFC 104]]\n| For the [[UFC Light Heavyweight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Lightweight\n| [[B.J. Penn]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Diego Sanchez]]\n| TKO (cut)\n| 5\n| 2:37\n| [[UFC 107]]\n| For the [[UFC Lightweight Championship]]\n}}\n{{MMAtitle end|notes = yes}}\n\n==The Ultimate Fighter==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:99%;\"\n!Season!!Finale!!Division!!Winner!!Runner-up\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:left\"|[[TUF 9|TUF 9: United States vs. United Kingdom]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[The Ultimate Fighter: United States vs. United Kingdom Finale|Jun 20, 2009]]\n|Lightweight\n| [[Ross Pearson]]\n| [[Andre Winner]]\n|-\n|Welterweight\n| [[James Wilks]]\n| [[DaMarques Johnson]]\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left\"|[[TUF 10|TUF 10: Heavyweights]]\n|[[The Ultimate Fighter: Heavyweights Finale|Dec 5, 2009]]\n|Heavyweight\n| [[Roy Nelson (fighter)|Roy Nelson]]\n| [[Brendan Schaub]]\n|}\n\n==Debut UFC fighters==\n\nThe following fighters fought their first UFC fight in 2009:\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Aaron Simpson (fighter)|Aaron Simpson]]\n*[[Alexander Gustafsson]]\n*Alexandre Barros\n*[[Andre Winner]]\n*[[Ant\u00f4nio Rog\u00e9rio Nogueira]]\n*[[Ben Rothwell]]\n*[[Brendan Schaub]]\n*Brian Cobb\n*[[Brian Foster (fighter)|Brian Foster]]\n*[[Brian Stann]]\n*[[Cameron Dollar (fighter)|Cameron Dollar]]\n*[[Carlos Condit]]\n*[[Chase Gormley]]\n*[[Chris Tuchscherer]]\n*[[DaMarques Johnson]]\n*[[Dan Cramer]]\n*[[Danillo Villefort]]\n*[[Darrill Schoonover]]\n*[[Denis Kang]]\n*Denis Stojnic\n*Derek Downey\n*[[Drew McFedries]]\n*[[Edgar Garcia]]\n*[[Evan Dunham]]\n*[[Fabricio Cam\u00f5es]]\n*[[Frank Lester (fighter)|Frank Lester]]\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Igor Pokrajac]]\n*Ivan Serati\n*[[Jacob Volkmann]]\n*[[Jake Ellenberger]]\n*[[Jake Rosholt]]\n*[[James McSweeney]]\n*[[James Wilks]]\n*[[Jared Hamman]]\n*[[Jay Silva]]\n*[[Jesse Lennox]]\n*Jesse Sanders\n*Joe Brammer\n*[[John Hathaway]]\n*[[John Howard (fighter)|John Howard]]\n*[[Johny Hendricks]]\n*[[Jon Madsen]]\n*[[Justin Wren]]\n*[[Kimbo Slice]]\n*Lucio Linhares\n*[[Marcus Jones (fighter)|Marcus Jones]]\n*[[Mark Munoz]]\n*[[Matt Mitrione]]\n*[[Matt Veach]]\n*Mike Ciesnolevicz\n*[[Mike Pierce]]\n*[[Mike Pyle (fighter)|Mike Pyle]]\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Mike Russow]]\n*[[Neil Grove]]\n*[[Nick Catone]]\n*[[Nick Osipczak]]\n*[[Nik Lentz]]\n*Nissen Osterneck\n*[[Paul Daley]]\n*[[Paulo Thiago]]\n*[[Peter Sobotta (fighter)|Peter Sobotta]]\n*[[Rafaello Oliveira]]\n*[[Ricardo Funch]]\n*[[Rick Story]]\n*[[Rodney Wallace (fighter)|Rodney Wallace]]\n*[[Ross Pearson]]\n*[[Roy Nelson (fighter)|Roy Nelson]]\n*Ryan Madigan\n*[[Stefan Struve]]\n*Steve Lopez\n*[[Steve Steinbeiss]]\n*[[Tim Hague]]\n*[[Tim McKenzie]]\n*[[TJ Grant]]\n*[[Todd Duffee]]\n*Tom Egan\n*Xavier Foupa-Pokam\n*[[Yoshihiro Akiyama]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Events list==\n{{Main article|List of UFC events}}\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable succession-box\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! scope=\"col\" | #\n! scope=\"col\" | Event\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n! scope=\"col\" | Venue\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Attendance\n|-\n|142\n|[[UFC 107|UFC 107: Penn vs. Sanchez]]\n|{{dts|2009|Dec|12}}\n|[[FedExForum]]\n|[[Memphis, Tennessee]], U.S.\n|{{nts|13896}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mmajunkie.com/news/17192/ufc-107-penn-vs-sanchez-draws-reported-13896-attendees-for-over-1-5-million-gate.mma |title=UFC 107 draws reported 13,896 attendees for \"over $1.5 million\" gate |publisher=mmajunkie.com |date=Dec 13, 2009 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013220613/http://mmajunkie.com/news/17192/ufc-107-penn-vs-sanchez-draws-reported-13896-attendees-for-over-1-5-million-gate.mma |archivedate=2012-10-13 }}</ref>\n|-\n|141\n|{{sort|Ultimate Fighter 10|[[The Ultimate Fighter: Heavyweights Finale]]}}\n|{{dts|2009|Dec|5}}\n|[[Palms Casino Resort]]\n|[[Las Vegas]], U.S.\n|{{nts|1791}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mmajunkie.com/news/17252/the-ultimate-fighter-10-finale-draws-1791-for-503600-gate.mma |title=The Ultimate Fighter 10 Finale draws 1,791 attendees for $503,600 gate |publisher=mmajunkie.com |date=Dec 17, 2009 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120525164447/http://mmajunkie.com/news/17252/the-ultimate-fighter-10-finale-draws-1791-for-503600-gate.mma |archivedate=2012-05-25 }}</ref>\n|-\n|140\n|[[UFC 106|U