agicon|Ireland}} [[Martin Donnelly (footballer, born 1951)|Martin Donnelly]]\n\n'''1980s'''\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Richard Kelly (footballer)|Richard Kelly]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Jerome Clarke]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Frank \"Dusty\" Flanagan]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Tony Macken]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Ray Treacy]]\n*{{flagicon|England}} [[Peter Barnes (footballer)|Peter Barnes]]\n\n'''2010s'''\n*{{flagicon|England}} [[Guy Bates]]\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Gavin Brennan]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Declan O'Brien (footballer)|Declan O'Brien]]\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Miche\u00e1l Schlingermann]]'''\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Keith Treacy]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Stephen Maher (footballer)|Stephen Maher]]\n\n{{col-4}}\n\n'''2000s'''\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Gary Rogers]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Bosnia & Herzegovina}} [[Fahrudin Kuduzovi\u0107]]\n*'''{{flagicon|Libya}} [[\u00c9amon Zayed]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Stephen Bradley (footballer)|Stephen Bradley]]\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Shaun Williams (footballer)|Shaun Williams]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Ollie Cahill]]\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[James Chambers (Irish footballer)|James Chambers]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Dan Connor (footballer)|Dan Connor]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Keith Fahey]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Graham Gartland]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Jason Gavin (footballer)|Jason Gavin]]\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Paul Keegan (footballer born 1984)|Paul Keegan]]'''\n*'''{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Conor Kenna]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Andrew Myler]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Shane Robinson (footballer)|Shane Robinson]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Brian Shelley]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[Simon Webb (footballer)|Simon Webb]]\n*{{flagicon|Wales}} [[Chris Todd]]\n*{{flagicon|Ireland}} [[David McAllister (footballer)|David McAllister]]\n*'''{{flagicon|Finland}} [[Mikko Vilmunen]]'''\n*{{flagicon|Australia}} [[Adam Hughes (footballer)|Adam Hughes]]\n*{{flagicon|Scotland}} [[Jamie Ewings]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Personnel==\n\n===Technical staff===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! style=\"color:#7EBFFF; background:#990033\"|Position\n! style=\"color:#7EBFFF; background:#990033\"|Staff\n|-\n| Director of Football || [[Dave Robertson (football manager)|Dave Robertson]]\n|-\n| Head Coach || [[Tim Clancy]]\n|-\n| Assistant Coach || [[Kevin Doherty (footballer)|Kevin Doherty]]\n|-\n| Doctor || Conor Kelly\n|-\n|  || \n|-\n| Groundsman || Matt Kavanagh\n|-\n| Kitman || Brendan Penrose/ Barry Sanfey\n|}\n\n===Management===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! style=\"color:#7EBFFF; background:#990033\"|Position\n! style=\"color:#7EBFFF; background:#990033\"|Staff\n|-\n| Honorary President || Vincent Hoey\n|-\n| Chairman || Conor Hoey\n|-\n| Secretary || \n|-\n| Finance officer || Martin Hodgins\n|-\n| Media officer || Robert O'Reilly\n|-\n| Delegate || Derek Kerr\n|}\n\n== Managerial history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Dates\n! Name\n! Honours\n|-\n| 1963\u201364\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Peter Farrell (Irish footballer)|Peter Farrell]]\n|\n|-\n| 1964\u201365\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Mick Lynch\n|\n|-\n| 1965\u201366\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Alf Girvan\n|\n|-\n| 1966\u201367\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Theo Dunne\n|\n|-\n| 1967\u201369\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Arthur Fitzsimons]] / Theo Dunne\n|\n|-\n| 1969\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Theo Dunne\n|\n|-\n| 1969\u201373\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Mick Meagan]]\n|\n|-\n| 1973\u201375\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} John Cowan\n|\n|-\n| 1975\u201378\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Jimmy McAlinden]]\n|\n|-\n| 1978\u201379\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Willie Roche\n|\n|-\n| 1979\u201380\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Shay Noonan\n|\n|-\n| 1980\u201382\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Ray Treacy]]\n|\n|-\n| 1982\u201385\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Tony Macken]]\n| [[League of Ireland Cup]] \u2013 1983\u201384\n|-\n| 1985\u201386\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Tony Reilly\n|\n|-\n| 1986\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Mick Lawlor (footballer)|Mick Lawlor]]\n|\n|-\n| 1987\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} Ciaran Maher\n|\n|-\n| 1987\u201388\n| {{flagicon|I