{"title_page": "2010 in UFC", "text_new": "{{short description|UFC MMA events in 2010}}\n{{Year in UFC\n|name = 2010 in UFC\n|image = Logo of the Ultimate Fighting Championship.svg\n|image_size = 176px\n|first_date = January 2, 2010\n|last_date = December 11, 2010\n|total_events = 24\n|numbered_events = 17\n|versus_events = 2\n|fight_night_events = 3\n|tuf_finale_events = 2\n|total_fights = 255\n|title_fights = 10\n|preceded_by = [[2009 in UFC]]\n|followed_by = [[2011 in UFC]]\n}}\n\nThe year '''2010''' is the 18th year in the history of the [[Ultimate Fighting Championship]] (UFC), a [[mixed martial arts]] promotion based in the United States. In 2010 the UFC held 24 events beginning with, ''UFC 108: Evans vs. Silva''.\n\n{{TOClimit|2}}\n\n==Title fights==\n{{MMAtitle}}\n{{MMAtitle card|[[List of UFC champions|Title fights in 2010]]}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Heavyweight\n| [[Shane Carwin]]\n| def.\n| [[Frank Mir]]\n| KO (punches)\n| 1\n| 3:48\n| [[UFC 111]]\n|\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Welterweight\n| [[Georges St-Pierre]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Dan Hardy]]\n| Decision (unanimous) (50\u201343, 50\u201344, 50\u201345)\n| 5\n| 5:00\n| [[UFC 111]]\n| \n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Lightweight\n| [[Frankie Edgar]]\n| def.\n| [[B.J. Penn]] (c)\n| Decision (unanimous) (50\u201345, 48\u201347, 49\u201346)\n| 5\n| 5:00\n| [[UFC 112]]\n| \n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Middleweight\n| [[Anderson Silva]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Demian Maia]]\n| Decision (unanimous) (49\u201347, 48\u201347, 49\u201346)\n| 5\n| 5:00\n| [[UFC 112]]\n| \n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Light Heavyweight\n| [[Maur\u00edcio Rua]]\n| def.\n| [[Lyoto Machida]] (c)\n| KO (punches)\n| 1\n| 3:35\n| [[UFC 113]]\n| \n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Heavyweight\n| [[Brock Lesnar]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Shane Carwin]] (ic)\n| Submission (arm-triangle choke)\n| 2\n| 2:19\n| [[UFC 116]]\n| \n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| Middleweight\n| [[Anderson Silva]] (c)\n| def\n| [[Chael Sonnen]]\n| Submission (triangle armbar)\n| 5\n| 3:10\n| [[UFC 117]]\n| \n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout