y]]\n*Jamie Yeager\n*[[Jason High]]\n*Jesse Bongfeldt\n*[[Joey Beltran]]\n*[[John Gunderson]]\n*[[John Makdessi]]\n*[[John Salter]]\n*[[Jonathan Brookins]]\n*Josh Bryant\n*Julio Paulino\n*[[Karlos Vemola]]\n*[[Kris McCray]]\n*[[Kurt Warburton]]\n*[[Kyle Noke]]\n*[[Kyle Watson]]\n*[[Maiquel Falc\u00e3o]]\n*[[Mario Miranda (fighter)|Mario Miranda]]\n*[[Mark Holst]]\n*[[Mark Hunt]]\n*Mark Scanlon\n*[[Michael Johnson (fighter)|Michael Johnson]]\n*[[Mike Guymon]]\n*Mike Lullo\n*[[Nam Phan]]\n*[[Nick Pace]]\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Pablo Garza (fighter)|Pablo Garza]]\n*[[Pascal Krauss]]\n*Pat Audinwood\n*[[Paul Sass]]\n*[[Phil Davis (fighter)|Phil Davis]]\n*[[Rafael Natal]]\n*[[Renzo Gracie]]\n*[[Ricardo Romero (fighter)|Ricardo Romero]]\n*[[Rich Attonito]]\n*[[Rob Broughton]]\n*[[Rolles Gracie Jr.]]\n*Ronys Torres\n*[[Rory MacDonald (fighter)|Rory MacDonald]]\n*[[Sako Chivitchian]]\n*[[Sean McCorkle]]\n*[[Sean Pierson]]\n*[[Seth Baczynski]]\n*T.J. O'Brien\n*[[T.J. Waldburger]]\n*[[Takanori Gomi]]\n*Todd Brown\n*[[Travis Browne]]\n*[[Tyler Toner]]\n*[[Vinicius Queiroz]]\n*[[Waylon Lowe]]\n*[[Will Campuzano]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Events List==\n{{Main article|List of UFC events}}\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable succession-box\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! scope=\"col\" | #\n! scope=\"col\" | Event\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n! scope=\"col\" | Venue\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Attendance\n|-\n|166\n|[[UFC 124|UFC 124: St-Pierre vs. Koscheck 2]]\n|{{dts|2010|Dec|11}}\n|[[Bell Centre]]\n|[[Montreal]], Canada\n|{{nts|23152}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mmajunkie.com/news/21722/ufc-124-draws-reported-record-attendance-of-23152-for-46-million-gate.mma |title=UFC 124 draws reported record attendance of 23,152 for $4.6 million gate |publisher=mmajunkie.com |date=Dec 11, 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023073817/http://mmajunkie.com/news/21722/ufc-124-draws-reported-record-attendance-of-23152-for-46-million-gate.mma |archivedate=2012-10-23 }